<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><title>rạfʿ rạyẗ</title>
<lyrics>[V1]
 ạlqrạr- rạfʿ rạyẗ bạlạ̉nạsẖyd rạsm frḥy ʿly ạlạ̉wtạr
 kl ḥyạty lltmjyd ạ̉nạ wạlʿwd lyswʿ ạlbạr
 1- (frḥ trnymạty byh ngẖmẗ fy ḍy ạlsmạwyạt
 nạdy ḥyạty ʿsẖạn tnạdyh sẖkr wḥmd wtsbyḥạt)2
 2- (frḥ ʿjyb gẖmr skyb fyḍ ạlḥb rfʿny ạ̹lyh
 rạyẗ ạlfrḥẗ ʿlyhạ ṣlyb hw ạlsr ạlly mkẖbyh)2
 3- (ʿhd ạlfrḥ mdy ạlạ̉yạm ʿhd slạmh lynạ ạ̉kyd
 mạt ʿlsẖạnạ yswʿnạ wqạm dạs ạlmwt wʿṭạnạ ạlʿyd)2
 4- (dwsy bʿz yạ nfsy kmạn dwsy mʿạh kl ạlậlạmạt
 ʿdy mʿạh fwq ạlạ̉ḥzạn dh ạlly ʿṭạky ạlḥryạt)2</lyrics>
<author>mạhr fạyz, mạhr fạyz</author>
<hymn_number>1583</hymn_number>
</song>